Text: TYSVM, do you also have "A First Course in Mathematical Modeling", 4th Edition by Frank R. Giordano, William P. Fox, Steven B. Horton and Maurice D. Weir?

I found the 3rd edition in DJVU format on Rapishare. Google the string
"first course mathematical modeling rapidlibrary". Size: 28~29 MB.
For a nice and powerful DJVU reader, google "windjview sourceforge".
Then you can index the Giordano textbook here on TPB.
